                            I N V A S I O N ! 

           (A Public Domain Adventure, author Robert Henderson)




SHUTTLE

(Bridge) S - S - S - S - E.



(Library) INSERT DISK - W - N - SW - D - D.



(Lab) TAKE SLIDE - TAKE KNIFE - CUT FINGER - UP - UP - NE - N - N - E.



(Transformation  device)   INSERT  SLIDE  -  DROP ALL - PRESS BUTTON - IN -

(Change into Xolsck) - OUT - TAKE ALL - W - S - E.



(Incinerator  unit)  THROW TROUSERS IN UNIT - THROW SHIRT IN UNIT - W - S -

S.



(Door)  SAY XOLSCK - (Door opens) - S - E - TAKE SUIT - W - N - N - N - N -

N.



(Bridge) TYPE TA11XA - PULL JOYSTICK.



MOTHERSHIP



(Living area) W.



(Small room) TAKE DIAMOND - EXAMINE CORNER - CUT WIRE - TAKE WIRE - E - E -

N - N - W.



(Living area/sleeping man) KILL MAN WITH WIRE - TAKE PASS - E - N.



(Corridor/by  locked  door)  UNSCREW  SCREWS WITH KNIFE - CONNECT LOCK WITH

WIRE  - (Door opens) - E - E - NE - E - S - W - S - W - S - SE - NE - S - S

- E - N - N - NW - E.



(Clearing) INSERT PASS - E.



(Small hut) TAKE COMPU-CART - TAKE LASER - W - W - SE - S - S - W - N - N -

SW - NW - N - E - N - E - N - W - SW - W - W - S - S - S - S.



(Controller)  INSERT  COMPU-CART  -  IN  -  DROP LASER - OUT - PRESS BUTTON

(Laser  charged) - IN - TAKE LASER - OUT - N - N - N - N - E - E - NE - E -

S - W - S - W - S - SE - NE - S - S - E - N - N - NW - E - N.



(Short  corridor/robot) CONNECT DIAMOND TO LASER - SHOOT ROBOT WITH LASER -

N.



(Security room) TAKE KEY - S - S - W - SE - S - S - W - W.



(By door) UNLOCK DOOR - S.



(Long  bridge) S - S - W - N - N - NW - SW - W - S - E - SE - SW - W - SE -

E  -  TAKE GLASS - W - NW - E - NE - NW - W - N - E - NE - SE - S - S - E -

E.



(Paint  room) IN - DROP GLASS - OUT - PRESS BUTTON - IN - TAKE MIRROR - OUT

- W - W - N - N - NW - SW - W - S - E - SE - SW - W - SE - E - E.



(Security door) S - W - W - S.



(Food machine) PRESS BUTTON - TAKE MEAT - N - E - E - E - E - S - S - E - E

- N - N - NW.



(Zoo/Grvvakk) THROW GRVVAKK THE MEAT - W.



(Research lab) TAKE PILLS - TAKE PHIAL - E - SE - S - S - W - W - N - N - W

- W - N.



(Security door) W - W - NW - E - NE - NW - W - N - E - NE.



(Bewildering maze/outside guard room) EAT PILL - THROW PHIAL NORTH - N.



(Guard room) TAKE GUN - S - SW - W - S - E - SE - SW - W - SE - E - E - S -

E - S.



(Security door/outside weapons section) SHOOT DOOR WITH GUN - S - S - S - W

- N - NW - N - E - N - W.



(Armoury door) TAKE ZELL - E - S - W - S - SE - S - E - N - N - DOWN - E.



(Corridor/guard) THROW ZELL AT GUARD - E



(Armoury control) PRESS BLUE BUTTON - (Opens armoury door) - W - W - UP - S

- S - W - N - NW - N - E - N - W - N.



(Armoury) EXAMINE BOMB - TYPE AZCT - S - E - S - W - S - SE - S - E - S.



(Teleport control) PRESS BUTTON - IN.............To complete the game!!



